<p>Let’s look at some data in <a href="../misc/xml_vs_json">JSON and XML</a>.</p>

<p>Any differences you notice?</p>

<ul>
  <li>XML slightly resembles HTML (both are markup languages)</li>
  <li>JSON has less overhead, therefore making it faster in many cases</li>
</ul>

